{"type":null,"faqId":10037,"title":"G6-U00如何设置自选音乐为来电/短信铃音？","answer":"&nbsp;\n<p style=\"text-indent:-12.2pt;margin-left:63.25pt;\" align=\"left\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"><span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">（1）</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">进入设置</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">-&gt;</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">声音</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">-&gt;SIM</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">卡</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">铃声</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">/ SIM</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">卡</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">铃声</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">-&gt;</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">音乐，修改来电铃声。</span><span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">（2）</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">进入设置</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">-&gt;</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">声音</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">-&gt;</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">通知铃声</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">-&gt;</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">消息通知铃声</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">-&gt;</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">音乐，修改信息铃声。</span></span> \n</p>\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=30575\" /> \n<p align=\"left\">\n\t&nbsp;\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-12.2pt;margin-left:63.25pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"><span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">（3</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">）</span><span style=\"fon